title: Sports Management Students Pursue Internships Opportunities (University of Minnesota - Morris)
text: ( Source : University of Minnesota - Morris ) Posted by Logan Bender '17, Red Wing on Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015 Last month eight sports management majors from the University of Minnesota, Morris visited the Twin Cities for an internship fair.
